<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="hero hero--subtle">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <span class="eyebrow">Enablement</span>
          <h1>Bhojan Mitra training &amp; launch playbooks</h1>
          <p>Founding partners receive end-to-end training — from voice scripting and kitchen routing to analytics deep dives. We run every pilot with hands-on workshops for owners, managers, and frontline teams.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Schedule a training consult</a>
            <a href="#programs" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Browse training tracks</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="programs" class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Training tracks</span>
        <h2>Guided sessions tailored to each role</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Service team onboarding</h3>
            <p>Teach waitstaff and cashiers how to use voice prompts, confirm orders, handle modifiers, and manage mid-service adjustments.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Kitchen &amp; expo workshops</h3>
            <p>Walk through KDS views, printer routing, and fallbacks. Practise ticket escalations and voice override flows during rush.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Manager analytics deep dive</h3>
            <p>Understand dashboards, set targets, export data, and configure alerts that keep covers, sales, and margins on track.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Owner strategy sessions</h3>
            <p>Define pilot goals, ROI models, and change management plans. Get templates for SOPs, staff incentives, and reviews.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ecosystem">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">What’s included</span>
        <div class="ecosystem-grid">
          <div class="eco-card">
            <h3>Live + recorded sessions</h3>
            <p>Interactive workshops plus a growing library of bite-sized videos your team can revisit anytime.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-card featured">
            <h3>In-shift support</h3>
            <p>Founders-on-call during your first busy shifts with Bhojan Mitra. We troubleshoot together in real time.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-card">
            <h3>Certification path</h3>
            <p>Certify team leads and trainers so future staff onboarding stays fast and consistent.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready to plan training for your pilot?</h2>
        <p>Share your staffing structure and we’ll propose a training calendar, materials, and support cadence.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Talk to the training team</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Review founding partner plans</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
